com.storytron.swat.verbeditor

Class ScriptEditor<ContainerState>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.storytron.swat.verbeditor.ScriptEditor<ContainerState>

  • public abstract class ScriptEditor<ContainerState>
extends java.lang.Object
    An editor for scripts.

    The script editor holds operator menus, a panel for shortcut buttons, and a header for identifying the edited script and accessing scriptalyzer.
